<h2>What's New</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Auto-update no longer fails with "An error occurred while launching the installer." The vendored Sparkle.framework was missing `Versions/B/Updater.app`, which Sparkle 2.7+ requires as its progress/authorization helper. Existing 0.014 and 0.015 installs have the same broken framework and must reinstall manually from this DMG to recover auto-update.</li></ul>
<p class="footer">DockishOS 0.016</p>
